description:
Stellar Blade is a PlayStation 5 exclusive from developer Shift Up, which puts players in control of Eve, a soldier sent to reclaim Earth from aliens known as the Naytiba. Thanks to the new demo, we got a taste of what this action-packed game has to offer, including combat, exploration, and an early boss fight. Here’s a taste of what players can expect when the full game launches on April 26, 2024.
